Labour Day
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: 1899 Act made it a public holiday on the 2nd Wednesday in Oct; until 1910 when the Public Holidays Act changed it to the 4th Monday in October.
